{"TopicId":188380,"ForumId":66,"TopicTitle":"KSP Loading... Preview: Action Groups in flight","CreatedByName":"St4rdust","CreatedById":196576,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-20T23:30:36Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"St4rdust","CreatedById":196576,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-20T23:30:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff; color:#1d1c1d; font-size:15px; text-align:left\u0022\u003EHey, Kerbonauts! We know you\u2019re excited about the 1.8 update, and we\u2019ve been listening to your feedback, so here\u0027s another preview. With 1.8, you can now check assigned action groups, edit them, and even add new ones!\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ccenter\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allow=\u0022accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022315\u0022 id=\u0022ips_uid_9597_4\u0022 width=\u0022560\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/quFbnUvPtPQ\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/center\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starhawk","CreatedById":131400,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-20T23:31:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*Like*\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHappy landings!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"St4rdust","CreatedById":196576,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-20T23:32:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223675195\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188380\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221569022289\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022131400\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Starhawk\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Starhawk said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*Like*\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHappy landings!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI cannot wait to see that! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GrandProtectorDark","CreatedById":183946,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-20T23:34:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA much needed addition.\u003Cbr\u003E\nGlad it is a thing now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Angelo Kerman","CreatedById":106975,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-20T23:34:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a major game changer, especially when you have multiple craft docked together and their action groups conflict. Now we can change them! Nice new feature.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ThatGuyWithALongUsername","CreatedById":140817,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-20T23:35:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*like*\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTHANK YOU\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"flart","CreatedById":181486,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-20T23:43:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a cool new feature.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso how about user defined names for the Action Groups, and a quick check in the new\u00A0window?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022KHRumhw.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002245.69\u0022 height=\u0022228\u0022 width=\u0022499\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/KHRumhw.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-09-21T00:27:09Z\u0022 title=\u002209/21/2019 12:27  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 21, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by flart\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-20T23:53:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike, like, like, a thousand times like!!!! I know I\u2019ve been asking and pushing for this for awhile! I\u2019m very glad you guys listened and acted! I\u00A0can\u2019t wait to try it out! I know, I have to wait anyways...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSince you guys are listening, next on my wish list is..... \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Alarm Clock (mod)\u0022\u003EKAC\u003C/abbr\u003E and TWP, integrated with your new maneuver node tweakamabobber? That\u0027s the low-hanging fruit, since those are\u00A0TriggerAu\u0027s babies...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, and maybe a little \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/155858-151-161-172-all-yall-continued-one-button-common-action-grouping/\u0026amp;tab=comments#comment-2941065\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EAll Y\u0027all\u003C/a\u003E while y\u0027all are at it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003ECan we have the like button back now pleeeease?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-09-21T00:07:51Z\u0022 title=\u002209/21/2019 12:07  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 21, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by StrandedonEarth\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sh1pman","CreatedById":147869,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-21T00:17:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223675203\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188380\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221569023635\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289439\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022StrandedonEarth\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 minutes ago, StrandedonEarth said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike, like, like, a thousand times like!!!! I know I\u2019ve been asking and pushing for this for awhile! I\u2019m very glad you guys listened and acted! I\u00A0can\u2019t wait to try it out! I know, I have to wait anyways...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSince you guys are listening, next on my wish list is..... \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Alarm Clock (mod)\u0022\u003EKAC\u003C/abbr\u003E and TWP, integrated with your new maneuver node tweakamabobber? That\u0027s the low-hanging fruit, since those are\u00A0TriggerAu\u0027s babies...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, and maybe a little \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/155858-151-161-172-all-yall-continued-one-button-common-action-grouping/\u0026amp;tab=comments#comment-2941065\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EAll Y\u0027all\u003C/a\u003E while y\u0027all are at it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003ECan we have the like button back now pleeeease?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Alarm Clock (mod)\u0022\u003EKAC\u003C/abbr\u003E is an obvious next step, but I\u2019d really like to see MechJeb-style advanced S.A.S. control: hold specific\u00A0direction, force roll, align docking ports, etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-21T00:24:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223675203\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188380\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221569023635\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289439\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022StrandedonEarth\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n28 minutes ago, StrandedonEarth said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, and maybe a little \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/155858-151-161-172-all-yall-continued-one-button-common-action-grouping/\u0026amp;tab=comments#comment-2941065\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EAll Y\u0027all\u003C/a\u003E while y\u0027all are at it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003ECan we have the like button back now pleeeease?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, I am contractually obligated to like all mentions of All Y\u0027All \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EAnd great job, Squad! I could see actually using action groups now. No, seriously that was actually the one thing that kept me from using them on a regular basis: My not realizing I wanted them until I was already mid-mission, or if I did make them beforehand, that I did something wrong in setting them up.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HafCoJoe","CreatedById":80363,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-21T00:24:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAwesome!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-21T01:36:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWho would\u0027ve thought that KSP\u0027s eighth year would have been the one in which we get all the cool stuff.\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223675201\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188380\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221569023008\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181486\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022flart\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, flart said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso how about user defined names for the Action Groups, and a quick check in the new\u00A0window?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FullMetalMachinist","CreatedById":156531,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-21T02:16:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve been taking an extended break from the forums and the game. This update looks to be the one to bring me back.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just have to say thank you to Squad for being one of the best developers out there, and for continuing to give us FREE STUFF!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-21T05:21:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTerrific, that\u2019s one significant stress factor made a lot less stressful. Looks like 1.8 is going to be something special!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"zer0Kerbal","CreatedById":190933,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-21T05:57:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyes. one more mod I don\u0027t need to install. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Alarm Clock (mod)\u0022\u003EKAC\u003C/abbr\u003E/TWP would be nice. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003Ejust sneak a peek at LGG\u003C/span\u003E\u0027s mod spreadsheet and throw a couple of darts at it each update...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:rep:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/rep.png\u0022 title=\u0022:rep:\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:funds:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/Funds.png\u0022 title=\u0022:funds:\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:science:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/science.png\u0022 title=\u0022:science:\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:targetpro:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/TargetPro20px.png\u0022 title=\u0022:targetpro:\u0022\u003E!!!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-09-21T05:58:20Z\u0022 title=\u002209/21/2019 05:58  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 21, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by zer0Kerbal\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Poodmund","CreatedById":128643,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-21T06:33:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis looks like a big QoL improvement. To be fair it should have been implemented a long time ago but it looks as thought this implementation has been done well and had been integrated into the stock game UI very well so kudos the the people that have been working on this module. I\u0027m sure it will be very well received.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne question, when editing action groups in flight, will we be able to move the camera around whilst the game is paused so that we can click on vessel parts more easily?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-21T07:24:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*me likey*\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis should have been in the game so long ago. But it\u2019s certainly nice to see it now! I\u2019ve got so many craft that I launched into deep space without remembering to assign action groups....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Urus28","CreatedById":182121,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-21T08:07:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExcellent !\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Delay","CreatedById":173586,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-21T09:05:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOut of all development studios out there, Squad possibly listens to their fanbase the most, or at least it\u0027s high up that list.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI never really had that big of a problem with action groups since I almost never assign any, but I can imagine how this is a massive relief to others!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust one question: In the video it seemed like gameplay is paused while you\u0027re studying your action groups. Did I see that right?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidCosmos","CreatedById":192336,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-21T09:10:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n#like\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lokachop","CreatedById":171474,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-21T09:12:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis seems like\u00A0a great idea, thank you squad!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TriggerAu","CreatedById":57838,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-21T09:36:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223675324\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188380\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221569047601\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022128643\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Poodmund\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Poodmund said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022 data-gramm=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis looks like a big QoL improvement. To be fair it should have been implemented a long time ago but it looks as thought this implementation has been done well and had been integrated into the stock game UI very well so kudos the the people that have been working on this module. I\u0027m sure it will be very well received.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne question, when editing action groups in flight, will we be able to move the camera around whilst the game is paused so that we can click on vessel parts more easily?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, can rotate and zoom the camera so you can select and configure\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Poodmund","CreatedById":128643,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-21T10:54:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223675363\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188380\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221569058569\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257838\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TriggerAu\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, TriggerAu said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, can rotate and zoom the camera so you can select and configure\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*Like* Awesome to hear.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(that pesky Like button needs to return soon...\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xurkitree","CreatedById":187694,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-21T11:57:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ndangit, why can\u0027t i like this i really needed this in my playthrough days ago and here it is.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-09-21T14:25:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223675324\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188380\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221569047601\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022128643\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Poodmund\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Poodmund said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo be fair it should have been implemented a long time ago...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI appreciate the honesty in the video showing posts asking for this from 2013.\u00A0 At least they\u0027re semi-aware how long this feature has been needed / requested.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s frustrating that it took 8 years, but relieving\u00A0that KSP is finally addressing some of the long standing issues like \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003Edv\u003C/abbr\u003E, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Thrust-to-weight ratio\u0022\u003Etwr\u003C/abbr\u003E, action groups, and art.\u00A0 There\u0027s still a few more glaring issues I\u0027d like resolved, but I am hopeful they\u0027ll be handled by the final update of KSP.\u00A0 Maybe after 9 years we\u0027ll finally have that complete game, and I really do look forward to it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223675353\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188380\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221569056735\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022173586\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Delay\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, Delay said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOut of all development studios out there, Squad possibly listens to their fanbase the most...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI suppose...\u00A0 For some of us, it\u0027s just frustrating how long it\u0027s taken\u00A0them to listen to us on some of these features.\u00A0 Maybe something changed internally, but I\u0027m pretty happy with the recent direction Squad has taken with the past few updates.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}